<ol>
  <li>
    <p>安装相关库</p>

    <p>akshare 的安装过程相对简单很多</p>

    <div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">pip</span> <span class="n">install</span> <span class="n">akshare</span>
